ement on 30 May Test Firing at Tyura Tam\n\nThe Guided Missile and Astronautics Intelligence Committee on 3 June submitted to the United States Intelligence Board the following conclusions on the 30 May Soviet missile test at Tyura Tam", "token_count": 44, "token_end_0based": 43, "token_start_0based": 0, "token_text": "i the communist bloc gmaic statement on 30 may test firing at tyura tam the guided missile and astronautics intelligence committee on 3 june submitted to the united states intelligence board the following conclusions on the 30 may soviet missile test at tyura tam", "unred_source_page": 7}
